snippet.title: Zack Snyder FIRES Amber Heard from Aquaman 2 (Fans Have Spoken)
snippet.description:
Welcome back to our channel, Fabulously Famous. Today we are here to talk about "Fans have Spoken" Zack Snyder FIRES Amber Heard from Aquaman 2. But before we get started, subscribe to our channel, to never miss any updates... So without any further delay, let’s get started quickly.

Amber Heard has finally caught herself in Big Trouble. Guess what? The Aquaman star actress is out of the 'Aquaman 2' sequel, basically, this is what the fans of Johnny Depp and other viewers expected from the Warner Brothers.

Hence, After the Aquaman title sequel release news is in trend, Amber Heard is once again exposed to a storm of criticism and hate from the viewers of the Warner bros.

As we already know, Fans have called on filmmakers to boycott Johnny Depp's ex-wife Amber Heard from the movies she has signed with Warner Bros, following a domestic abuse lawsuit. 

Amber Heard and her ex-husband Johnny Depp are engaged in the hashtag Boycott Aquaman 2, and Johnny Depp's justice became a hot topic on Twitter shortly after the announcement.
